pedia.org/resource/OLPC_XO\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OLPC_XO\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one X chromosome\", \"from\": 4269, \"to\": 4285}, {\"ngram\": \"an extra chromosome\", \"from\": 4309, \"to\": 4328}, {\"ngram\": \"XXY\", \"from\": 4330, \"to\": 4333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their internal and external sex organs can be either male or female, but they may not go through full physical development at puberty.\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their internal and external sex organs\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4375}, {\"ngram\": \"full physical development\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4459}, {\"ngram\": \"puberty\", \"from\": 4463, \"to\": 4470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, a child with female sex organs may not start having periods.\", \"from\": 4472, \"to\": 4545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 4476, \"to\": 4483}, {\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 4485, \"to\": 4492}, {\"ngram\": \"female sex organs\", \"from\": 4498, \"to\": 4515}, {\"ngram\": \"periods\", \"from\": 4537, \"to\": 4544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Doctors tend to check a baby for DSD soon after birth if they are showing signs such as undescended testicles or if a baby's genitals look different.\", \"from\": 4547, \"to\": 4696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4580, \"end\": 4583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"score\": 0.9911850460161837, \"rank\": 0.008893348440711036, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Doctors\", \"from\": 4547, \"to\": 4554}, {\"ngram\": \"a baby\", \"from\": 4569, \"to\": 4575}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 4595, \"to\": 4600}, {\"ngram\": \"signs\", \"from\": 4621, \"to\": 4626}, {\"ngram\": \"undescended testicles\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4656}, {\"ngram\": \"a baby's genitals\", \"from\": 4663, \"to\": 4680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tests including ultrasounds and blood tests can be done before a baby's sex is registered.\", \"from\": 4697, \"to\": 4787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tests\", \"from\": 4697, \"to\": 4702}, {\"ngram\": \"ultrasounds\", \"from\": 4713, \"to\": 4724}, {\"ngram\": \"blood tests\", \"from\": 4729, \"to\": 4740}, {\"ngram\": \"a baby's sex\", \"from\": 4760, \"to\": 4772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many forms of DSD do not require any medical care other than understanding the baby's development and knowing what to expect as they grow older.\", \"from\": 4789, \"to\": 4933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4803, \"end\": 4806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"score\": 0.9911850460161837, \"rank\": 0.008893348440711036, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many forms\", \"from\": 4789, \"to\": 4799}, {\"ngram\": \"any medical care\", \"from\": 4822, \"to\": 4838}, {\"ngram\": \"the baby's development\", \"from\": 4864, \"to\": 4886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other people with DSD are sometimes only diagnosed once puberty begins and it becomes clear something is not right.\", \"from\": 4935, \"to\": 5050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4953, \"end\": 4956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"score\": 0.9911850460161837, \"rank\": 0.008893348440711036, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other people\", \"from\": 4935, \"to\": 4947}, {\"ngram\": \"puberty\", \"from\": 4991, \"to\": 4998}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5027, \"to\": 5036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The issue has caused a lot of people toshare their opinions on the matter.\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The issue\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5061}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 5073, \"to\": 5078}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5082, \"to\": 5088}, {\"ngram\": \"their opinions\", \"from\": 5097, \"to\": 5111}, {\"ngram\": \"the matter\", \"from\": 5115, \"to\": 5125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some commentators have said it is wrong for a person who is considered biologically as strong as a man to compete against a biological woman, as it would give an unfair advantage.\", \"from\": 5127, \"to\": 5306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some commentators\", \"from\": 5127, \"to\": 5144}, {\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5179}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 5224, \"to\": 5229}, {\"ngram\": \"a biological woman\", \"from\": 5249, \"to\": 5267}, {\"ngram\": \"an unfair advantage\", \"from\": 5286, \"to\": 5305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former GB swimmer Sharron Daviessaid: \\\"This is a biological male fighting a female & absolutely everyone can see it, they have also failed gender screening, twice & have XY chromosomes.\", \"from\": 5308, \"to\": 5493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5315, \"end\": 5317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999823091839575, \"rank\": 1.7690904083769933e-05, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a biological male\", \"from\": 5355, \"to\": 5372}, {\"ngram\": \"a female\", \"from\": 5382, \"to\": 5390}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 5404, \"to\": 5412}, {\"ngram\": \"gender screening\", \"from\": 5447, \"to\": 5463}, {\"ngram\": \"XY chromosomes\", \"from\": 5478, \"to\": 5492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no ambiguity that the IOC do not care if a female gets seriously hurt.\", \"from\": 5494, \"to\": 5573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5525, \"end\": 5528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.113333803259931e-42, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no ambiguity\", \"from\": 5503, \"to\": 5515}, {\"ngram\": \"a female\", \"from\": 5544, \"to\": 5552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or worse.\", \"from\": 5574, \"to\": 5583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am astonished at the weakness of the media.\\\"\", \"from\": 5584, \"to\": 5630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weakness\", \"from\": 5603, \"to\": 5615}, {\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 5619, \"to\": 5628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A string of MPs made similar condemnations.\", \"from\": 5632, \"to\": 5675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A string\", \"from\": 5632, \"to\": 5640}, {\"ngram\": \"MPs\", \"from\": 5644, \"to\": 5647}, {\"ngram\": \"similar condemnations\", \"from\": 5653, \"to\": 5674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anna Turley, Labour MP for Redcar, said: \\\"This is just not acceptable @Olympics - enough.\\\"\", \"from\": 5677, \"to\": 5767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5677, \"end\": 5688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Turley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Turley\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Turley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Turley\"}, {\"begin\": 5704, \"end\": 5710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Redcar_Racecourse\", \"score\": 0.9878