ional_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.113333803259931e-42, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the name\", \"from\": 5931, \"to\": 5939}, {\"ngram\": \"sanity\", \"from\": 5943, \"to\": 5949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Pierre de Coubertin said 'all sports for all people' he would never have intended for men fighting women to be one of those sports.\", \"from\": 5980, \"to\": 6116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5985, \"end\": 6004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pierre de Coubertin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all sports\", \"from\": 6011, \"to\": 6021}, {\"ngram\": \"all people\", \"from\": 6026, \"to\": 6036}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 6071, \"to\": 6074}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6084, \"to\": 6089}, {\"ngram\": \"those sports\", \"from\": 6103, \"to\": 6115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Male violence on females cannot be tolerated as a spectatorsport.\\\"\", \"from\": 6117, \"to\": 6183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Male violence\", \"from\": 6117, \"to\": 6130}, {\"ngram\": \"females\", \"from\": 6134, \"to\": 6141}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectatorsport\", \"from\": 6165, \"to\": 6181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Thursday morning, Mark Adams, an IOC spokesman, said those competing in the boxing are compliant with the eligibility rules.\", \"from\": 6185, \"to\": 6312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6206, \"end\": 6216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"score\": 0.5137413298826524, \"rank\": 0.45833333333