itions\", \"from\": 6614, \"to\": 6651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The IOC is saddened by the abuse that the two athletes are currently receiving.\", \"from\": 6654, \"to\": 6734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6659, \"end\": 6662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.113333803259931e-42, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the abuse\", \"from\": 6678, \"to\": 6687}, {\"ngram\": \"the two athletes\", \"from\": 6693, \"to\": 6709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IBA's recognition was withdrawn by the IOC in 2023 following its suspension in 2019.\\\"\", \"from\": 6735, \"to\": 6824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6739, \"end\": 6742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999998432986227, \"rank\": 1.567017860267551e-07, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 6778, \"end\": 6781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.113333803259931e-42, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its suspension\", \"from\": 6800, \"to\": 6814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South African runner and Olympic gold medallist Caster Semenya has a DSD called 5-alpha-reductase deficiency, which means she has the male XY chromosomes and produces higher levels of testosterone than normal for women.\", \"from\": 6826, \"to\": 7045, \"entities