he has previously detailed how she has internal testes and no uterus, but does have a vagina.\", \"from\": 7146, \"to\": 7240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"internal testes\", \"from\": 7186, \"to\": 7201}, {\"ngram\": \"no uterus\", \"from\": 7206, \"to\": 7215}, {\"ngram\": \"a vagina\", \"from\": 7231, \"to\": 7239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Semenya, who dominated women's running events between 2009 and 2019, learned at the same time as the rest of the world that she had a DSD.\", \"from\": 7242, \"to\": 7380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7376, \"end\": 7379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"score\": 0.9911850460161837, \"rank\": 0.008893348440711036, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Semenya\", \"from\": 7242, \"to\": 7249}, {\"ngram\": \"women's running events\", \"from\": 7265, \"to\": 7287}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 7322, \"to\": 7335}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 7339, \"to\": 7347}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 7351, \"to\": 7360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was forced to take drugs such as the contraceptive pill to lower her testosterone to align with new rules that limited the level of the hormone in women's events.\", \"from\": 7381, \"to\": 7547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drugs\", \"from\": 7404, \"to\": 7409}, {\"ngram\": \"the contraceptive pill\", \"from\": 7418, \"to\": 7440}, {\"ngram\": \"her testosterone\", \"from\": 7450, \"to\": 7466}, {\"ngram\": \"new rules\", \"from\": 7481, \"to\": 7490}, {\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 7504, \"to\": 7513}, {\"ngram\": \"the hormone\", \"from\": 7517, \"to\": 7528}, {\"ngram\": \"women's events\", \"from\": 7532, \"to\": 7546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fellow runners Francine Niyonsaba of Burundi, Kenya's Margaret Nyairera Wambui and Namibia's Christine Mboma and Beatrice Masilingi have also been ruled ineligible to compete in competitions due to DSDs.\", \"from\": 7549, \"to\": 7752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7564, \"end\": 7582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francine_Niyonsaba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Francine Niyonsaba\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francine_Niyonsaba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francine_Niyonsaba\"}, {\"begin\": 7586, \"end\": 7593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burundi\", \"score\": 0.9999999844858395, \"rank\": 1.5514359027216248e-08, \"text\": \"Burundi\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burundi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burundi\"}, {\"begin\": 7595, \"end\": 7600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999997777404379, \"rank\": 2.2225648108097317e-07, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 7603, \"end\": 7627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margaret_Wambui\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Margaret Nyairera Wambui\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margaret_Wambui\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margaret_Wambui\"}, {\"begin\": 7632, \"end\": 7639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Namibia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.594006195777391e-15, \"text\": \"Namibia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Namibia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Namibia\"}, {\"begin\": 7642, \"end\": 7657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Mboma\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Christine Mboma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", 